{"word":"G5584 - ψηλαφάω - psēlapháō - psay-laf-ah'-o - Feel after","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ψηλαφάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">psēlapháō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">psay-laf-ah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Feel after</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தொடு, தடவு"},{"paragraph":"to handle, touch, feel"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the base of <a href=\"#/G5567 - ψάλλω - psállō - psal'-lo/5567\">G5567</a> (compare <a href=\"#/G5586 - ψῆφος - psēphos - psay'-fos/5586\">G5586</a>); to <i>manipulate</i>, that is, <i>verify</i> by contact; figuratively to <i>search</i> for: - feel after, handle, touch.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}